title: The Crochet Closet - 15 Designs to Enhance Your Wardrobe
description: Do you dream of opening your closet each day and finding the perfect outfit ready and waiting? If you crochet, you can make that dream a reality! These feminine fashions by Lisa Gentry give you the key pieces to finish any outfit with unique flair and confidence. For work or play, pair your favorite slacks and jeans with dressy or casual sweaters, vests, and jackets. Add a lacy shawl to your little black dress to get eye-catching results. Fun, figure-enhancing, casual, or elegant--the look that suits your mood is yours with crochet!
